        "exhibit_2_intro_title" : "Exhibition Introduction",        
        "exhibit_2_introduce_name" : "2nd Exhibition 07.01.-09.19.",
        "exhibit_2_introduce" : "The second exhibition of 2026 at Seoullo Media Canvas welcomes visitors with diverse perspectives on the city, nature, and emerging young creators set against the backdrop of midsummer. The exhibition consists of two sections: the Nature Project Exhibition and the University Collaboration Exhibition, presenting media artworks that explore the evolving urban landscape, the cycles of nature, and the fresh perspectives of a new generation.",
